name: Burton Morgan
text: This is the first Mac that I have used. I have only ever had a Lenovo and was skeptical to switch to apple despite having all other apple devices. I wasn't sure if I wanted to take the chance on hating it (since its so expensive) just to have the added perks of all of my devices connecting together. However, after hearing enough good reviews from friends I decided to switch and it was the best decision!

name: Tyler Harper
text: It is a great personal computer. Went with the touch bar and 256gb because it was on sale. Definitely go with more storage because nowadays to back up your phone you will need at least 128gb.
